Title: Clip Paris Swarovski Elements Pageant Bridal Crown Hair Barrette gold plated
Description: ~~~Welcome to My Store! ~~~ Be sure to check out my ME page for my blog and my stores Item Description This listing is for one stunning crown shaped hair barrette made from a gold plated base metal. It is self adjusting and a French clip barrette style- Made in France by Clip Paris- the mechanism style is also called a french clip. It is adorned with sparkling clear color genuine Swarovski Crystal elements and Aurora Borealis Crystals. It measures 3 3/4 inches wide by 1 1/2 inches top to bottom. It sits 3/4 inch high and the barrette mechanism on the back is 2 3/4 inches long. The barrette is self adjusting to hold all thickness' of hair. It has a graceful head hugging curve to it. Absolutely stunning and perfect for a bride, pageant, prom or any special occasion!See additional photos at the top left of this ad. Brand new and in perfect condition and sent boxed.
